'''''Daar doer in die bosveld''''' (Icyongereza: ''Far Away in Bushveld'' ) niyo film yambere yakozwe [[Afurika y’Epfo|numuyobozi wumunya Afrika yepfo]] Jamie Uys . Yasohotse bwa mbere mu 1951. <ref name="imdb">[[imdbtitle:0270903|imdb]]</ref> Filime iri mu [[Ikinyafurikansi|rurimi rwa Afrikaans]], ururimi rwihariye rwa [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ni urwenya ku muhinzi ufite isoni witwa Hans Botha usabwa gufata umwarimu ukiri muto witwa Martie du Toit. Hans ageze aho bisi ihagarara gufata Martie arumirwa rwose kubera ubwiza bwe kandi abasha kuvuga gusa interuro, "It looks like rain.." na It was an accident." Bombi bahura ningorane nyinshi munzira; ahanini bitewe n'imodoka ya kera ya Hans. Igihe bombi bageze aho Martie yerekeza, Martie atose kandi yemeza ko Hans ari igicucu. Hans, ariko, akunda byimazeyo Martie. 

